<Base title="Kraft Heinz — Case Study">

  <div class="section">
    <a class="breadcrumb" href="/Personal/case-studies/">← <span>Case Studies</span> / Kraft Heinz</a>
    <div class="cs-hero">[MiO Amazon A+ page or digital shelf visual]</div>
    <div class="cs-tags"><span class="cs-tag">Art direction</span><span class="cs-tag">eCommerce</span><span class="cs-tag">UX/UI</span><span class="cs-tag">CPG</span></div>
    <div class="cs-title">Kraft Heinz — Digital shelf and eComm creative</div>
    <div class="cs-subtitle">Art Director at Imaginary Content, embedded on the Kraft Heinz account. Led digital shelf transformation for MiO, produced 800+ digital assets, and designed 15 Amazon A+ pages across ~30 KH brands.</div>
    <div class="cs-meta-card">
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Client</div><div class="cs-meta-value">Kraft Heinz via Imaginary</div></div>
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Duration</div><div class="cs-meta-value">Feb 2020 – Oct 2021</div></div>
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Role</div><div class="cs-meta-value">Art Director</div></div>
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Brands</div><div class="cs-meta-value">MiO, Oscar Mayer, ~30 total</div></div>
